Total outbreaks: 3
Total animals affected:
Species / Susceptible / Cases / Deaths / Destroyed / Slaughtered
Birds / 78 / 34 / 0 / - / -

Outbreak statistics [rates apparent, expressed as percentages]:
Species / Morbidity rate / Mortality rate / Case fatality rate / Proportion susceptible animals lost*
Birds / 43.59 / 0 / 0 / **
*Removed from the susceptible population through death, destruction, and/or slaughter
**Not calculated because of missing information

Epidemiology
Source of the outbreak(s) or origin of infection: unknown or inconclusive; introduction of new live animals.
Epidemiological comments: Hobby farms with chickens and turkeys.

Control measures
Measures applied: movement control inside the country; no vaccination; no treatment of affected animals
Measures to be applied: no other measures

Diagnostic test results
Laboratory name and type: Finnish Food Safety Authority (Evira) (national laboratory)
Species / Test / Test date / Result
Birds / enzyme-linked immunosorbent assay (ELISA) / 8 Jun 2015 / Positive
Birds / real-time PCR / 8 Jun 2015 / Positive

Future reporting
The event is continuing. Weekly follow-up reports will be submitted.

