Epidemiology
Source of the outbreak(s) or origin of infection: unknown or inconclusive
Epidemiological comments: Hobby farms with chickens and turkeys. Haapavesi and Jamsa farms were also _M. gallisepticum_ infection positive at the same time.

Control measures
Measures applied: no vaccination; no treatment of affected animals
Measures to be applied: no other measures

Diagnostic test results
Laboratory name and type: Finnish Food Safety Authority (Evira) (national laboratory)
